  <brief_title>Personalized Treatment of Glioblastoma Via Image-Guided Predictive Modeling of Recurrence: A Single-Arm, Single Institutional Pilot Prospective Study of Dose-Escalated Radiation Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Personalized Treatment of Glioblastoma Via Image-Guided Predictive Modeling of Recurrence: A Single-Arm, Single Institutional Pilot Prospective Study of Dose-Escalated Radiation Therapy</official_title>
